quran[4{c,v,t}:
9,69,"tum logon ke rang dhang wohi hain jo tumahray paish roon ke thay woh tum se ziyada zor aawar aur tum se barh kar maal aur aulaad walay thay phir unhon ne duniya mein apne hissa ke mazay lout liye aur tum ne bhi apne hissay ke mazay isi terhan lautay jaisay unhon ne lautay thay, aur waisi hi bhson mein tum bhi parre jaisi bhson mein woh parre thay, so un ka injaam yeh howa ke duniya aur akhirat mein un ka sab kya dhara zaya ho gaya aur wohi khasaray mein hain"
9,70,"kya inn logon ko apne paish roon ki tareekh nahi pohanchi? Nooh ki qoum, Aad , smod, ibrahim ki qoum, Mudin ke log aur woh bastiyan jinhein ulat diya gaya unn ke rasool un ke paas khuli khuli nishanain le kar aeye, phir yeh Allah ka kaam nah tha ke un par zulm karta magar woh aap hi apne oopar zulm karne walay thay"
9,71,"momin mard aur momin aurtain, yeh sab aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain, bhalai ka hukum dete aur buraiee se roktay hain, namaz qaim karte hain, zkoh dete hain aur Allah aur is ke rasool ki itaat karte hain yeh woh log hain jin par Allah ki rehmat nazil ho kar rahay gi, yaqeenan Allah sab par ghalib aur hakeem o Dana hai"
9,72,"un momin mardon aur aurton se Allah ka wada hai ke inhen aisay baagh day ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi aur woh un mein hamesha rahen ge un sada bahhar baghoon mein un ke liye pakeeza qiyam gahin hon gi, aur sab se barh kar yeh ke Allah ki khushnodi inhen haasil hogi yahi barri kamyabi hai"
